items.content_html: Ria Retty doesnt just focus on food , She also has an interest for talent . "most young people lack moral support when it comes to talent and its up to a few people like me who can help know how and where to generate this positive energy " Ria says, she is a songwriter and a poet herself and most of her spokenword has hit the top bars like; slayqueen , wonder , utoi and many more .
